## Deployed API base (mobile)

`https://streamquiz.netlify.app`

- `POST /api/generate-questions`
- `POST /api/check-answer`
- `GET /api/ice-servers`

## Supabase

Realtime on `games` and `players`. WebRTC signaling: broadcast channel `webrtc:{gameId}` with presence. Max 6 players.

## Compatibility rules

- Do not rename or remove the API routes above without updating the Swift app.
- Do not change `games` / `players` columns or phase flow without updating native `GameStateManager`.
- Publishable key is client-safe; keep AI keys server-only.

When changing the web app, preserve native iOS compatibility unless the user explicitly says otherwise.
